Package: richR
Type: Package
Title: Functional Enrichment Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kai", "Guo", email = "guokai8@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Junguk", "Hur", email = "junguk.hur@med.und.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0736-2149"))
  )
Description: Performs functional enrichment analysis for Gene Ontology (GO),
    KEGG pathways, Reactome, and MSigDB gene sets. Supports over-representation
    analysis (ORA) via hypergeometric testing, Gene Set Enrichment Analysis (GSEA),
    and kappa-score-based term clustering. Provides publication-ready
    visualizations including bar plots, dot plots, network graphs, heatmaps,
    and cluster plots.
